   "source": [
    "### Average method"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 6,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "<matplotlib.image.AxesImage at 0x7f86a0a1a220>"

     "execution_count": 6,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    },
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 432x288 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {
      "needs_background": "light"
     },
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "gray_img = np.mean(img,axis=2)\n",
    "plt.imshow(gray_img,cmap='gray')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Weighted method or luminosity method\n",
    "\n",
    "- 0.2989 R + 0.5870 G + 0.1140 B"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 5,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "<matplotlib.image.AxesImage at 0x7f86a0a2b910>"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 5,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    },
    {
     "data": {
      "image/png": "\n",
      "text/plain": [
       "<Figure size 432x288 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {
      "needs_background": "light"
     },
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "B, G, R = img[...,0], img[...,1], img[...,2]\n",
    "\n",
    "imgGray = 0.2989 * R + 0.5870 * G + 0.1140 * B\n",
    "gray_img = ( 0.21 * R ) + (0.72 * G ) + ( 0.07 * B)\n",
    "plt.imshow(gray_img,cmap='gray')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
